title: DOCTOR STRANGE v1 v2 v3 and STRANGE TALES Complete 1963-2011
description:
Stephen Strange is Doctor Strange. But he is no longer a doctor, and least not the kind that would initially come to mind. He is the Master of the Mystic Arts, a sorcerer supreme, a white knight who wields black magic against blacker villains still. Strange is mankind's only hope against the dark otherworldly forces that conspire to destroy the conscious world - forces such as Baron Mordo, the Dread Dormammu, Nightmare, Aggamon, The House of Shadows, Loki, the Mindless Ones and more!
